        <abstract>
            <p>Is Bentham’s list of aberrant genera biased by exclusion of genera with many species?</p> 
<p>JDH’s belief that <hi rend="italic">Aquilegia</hi> varieties are one species is consistent with their great interfertility.</p> 
        </abstract>
